Title: Babysitting
Writer: Julien Arruti (screenplay), Tarek Boudali (screenplay), Philippe Lacheau (screenplay), Pierre Lacheau (screenplay)
Actors: Philippe Lacheau, Alice David, Vincent Desagnat, Tarek Boudali
Plot: What was supposed to be a quiet night of babysitting a boy, turns into a complete chaos after a few babysitter's friends arrive.
